<HL>
   Business Brief -- Pacific Telesis Group:
   Pacific Bell Unit Terminates
   Billing for Dial-a-Porn Calls
</HL>
<DATE>
10/16/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
